        'rss_summary': '<div><img src="https://www.gbnews.com/media-library/electric-car-charger.jpg?id=50301390&amp;width=1200&amp;height=600&amp;coordinates=0%2C0%2C0%2C953" style="width: 100%;" /><div>AA recorded only five or six EV breakdowns per year due to running out of battery</div></div>',
