        'rss_summary': '<div><img src="https://i2-prod.coventrytelegraph.net/incoming/article30365320.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200/0_A46-blanked-plates.jpg" style="width: 100%;" /><div>Coventry Live readers have been sharing their views on speed limits as the A46 from the M6, as after the Binley flyover, the speed limit suddenly drops from 70 to 50</div></div>',
        'link': 'https://www.coventrytelegraph.net/news/news-opinion/accident-waiting-happen-major-coventry-30407900',
