        'rss_summary': '<div><img src="https://www.stourbridgenews.co.uk/resources/images/18770391/" style="width: 100%;" /><div>The number of public electric vehicle chargers drivers had access to in Dudley fell by a tenth last year, new figures show.</div></div>',
        'link': 'https://www.stourbridgenews.co.uk/news/24732615.number-ev-chargers-dudley-fell-tenth-last-year/',
        'id': 'f26bcb380fd403f6968462709196213f',
        'authors': [
